    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔航空：电子商务繁荣将推动货运量增长 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/e-commerce-boom-to-drive-10-freight-growth-qatar-airways-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔航空货运部门表示，购物者对快速送货的强烈需求将推动今年航空货运量增长 10%，抵消主要经济体经济可能放缓带来的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/e-commerce-boom-to-drive-10-freight-growth-qatar-airways-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 04:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国铜金公司继续大举投资，斥资 19 亿美元入股锂矿商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/zijin-mining-to-buy-china-lithium-miner-stake-for-1-9-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紫金矿业集团股份有限公司是一家具有收购精神的中国铜和黄金生产商，该公司已同意以 19 亿美元收购一家国内矿业公司约四分之一的股份，以拓展锂业业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/zijin-mining-to-buy-china-lithium-miner-stake-for-1-9-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 14:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者质疑 IT 复苏速度，印孚瑟斯股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-on-rising-it-services-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印孚瑟斯公司 (Infosys Ltd.) 的销售预测低于分析师预期，导致其股价下跌，表明信息技术服务需求的复苏是渐进的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-on-rising-it-services-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 10:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
